    • read

      public static RDFPatch read(InputStream input)
      Read input stream and produce an RDFPatch. This operation actively reads the patch into memory. See read(InputStream, RDFChanges) to stream it to a chnage processor. Create an PatchReaderBinary object with create(java.io.InputStream) to create a delayed read processor. See RDFPatchOps.collect(org.apache.jena.rdfpatch.RDFPatch) to make sure a patch has been read.
